---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Eğitmen — Dr. Murat Altun"
  description="Veri Bilimi ve Yapay Zeka Uzmanlığı Programı eğitmeni Dr. Murat Altun hakkında. 20+ yıl eğitmenlik deneyimi, MEB ders kitabı yazarı, TÜBİTAK danışmanı."
  canonical="https://drmurataltun.github.io/meb-yegitek-derin-ogrenme/egitmen/"
>

  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="text-xs text-mid mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href={base} class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Program</a>
    <span class="mx-1">›</span>
    <span class="text-dark font-medium">Eğitmen Hakkında</span>
  </nav>

  <!-- Profil Kartı -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-border overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <!-- Kapak Barı -->
    <div class="h-28 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent"></div>

    <div class="px-8 pb-8 -mt-14">
      <!-- Avatar + İsim -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-end">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-2xl bg-warmBg border-4 border-white shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left md:pb-1">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">Dr. Murat Altun</h1>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm font-medium">Yapay Zeka Eğitmeni · Veri Bilimci · Yazar</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Biyografi -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-mid leading-relaxed">
        Bilişim Teknolojileri öğretmeni, yapay zeka eğitmeni ve 6 kitap yazarı.
        Eğitim teknolojileri, veri madenciliği ve yapay zeka alanlarında uzmanlaşmış <strong class="text-dark">20+ yıl eğitmenlik deneyimine</strong> sahip öğretmen-akademisyen.
        Akdeniz Üniversitesi'nde doktora çalışmalarını <strong class="text-dark">Eğitsel Veri Madenciliği</strong> üzerine tamamlamıştır.
        TÜBİTAK proje yürütücüsü ve danışmanıdır.
      </p>

      <!-- Sosyal Linkler -->
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/DrMuratAltun" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-border text-xs text-mid hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/drmurataltun" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-border text-xs text-mid hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Murat-Altun" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-border text-xs text-mid hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19.586 0c-1.225 0-2.236.547-2.94 1.32-.704.773-1.125 1.758-1.344 2.62-.219.86-.234 1.57-.234 2.06v.56h-3.5v3.44h3.5v14h4v-14h3.14l.46-3.44h-3.6v-.56c0-.22.02-.58.14-1.02.12-.44.36-.96.88-1.34.52-.38 1.2-.6 2.04-.6.56 0 1.08.08 1.46.16l.42-3.32c-.56-.12-1.36-.24-2.42-.24-.2 0-.4.01-.6.02V0h-.4z"/></svg>
          ResearchGate
        </a>
        <a href="https://drmurataltun.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-border text-xs text-mid hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"/></svg>
          Web Sitesi
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:emurataltun@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-border text-xs text-mid hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          E-posta
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detay Grid -->
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 mb-8">

    <!-- Akademik Geçmiş -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
        Akademik Geçmiş
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark">Doktora — Eğitsel Veri Madenciliği</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-mid">Akdeniz Üniversitesi, 2019</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark">Yüksek Lisans — Eğitim Yönetimi</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-mid">Veri Madenciliği ile Öğrenci Performans Tahmini</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-2 shrink-0"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark">Bilişim Teknolojileri Öğretmeni</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-mid">MEB — 20+ yıl öğretmenlik deneyimi</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Uzmanlık Alanları -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
        Uzmanlık Alanları
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {["Yapay Zeka", "Makine Öğrenmesi", "Derin Öğrenme", "Veri Bilimi", "Python", "Doğal Dil İşleme", "Eğitsel Veri Madenciliği", "Robotik Kodlama", "Bilgisayarlı Görü", "Generative AI"].map(tag => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-warmBg text-dark border border-border">
            {tag}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Başarılar & Kimlik -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/></svg>
        Başarılar & Deneyim
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        {[
          "MEB resmi ders kitabı yazarı (Yapay Zeka ve Makine Öğrenmesi)",
          "6 kitap yazarı (Python, YZ, Robotik Kodlama)",
          "10.000+ katılımcıya 50+ farklı eğitim programı",
          "TÜBİTAK proje yürütücüsü ve danışmanı",
          "BTK Akademi, DeneYap, Tech İstanbul eğitmeni",
          "500+ öğretmene YZ/ChatGPT eğitimi",
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-mid">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Eğitim Kurumları -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
        Eğitim Verilen Kurumlar
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {["MEB", "BTK Akademi", "DeneYap Atölyeleri", "Tech İstanbul", "Akdeniz Üniversitesi", "Antalya İl MEM", "TÜBİTAK", "Üniversiteler", "Teknoparklar"].map(org => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium bg-primary/5 text-primary border border-primary/10">
            {org}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <!-- Diğer Platformlar -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-border p-6 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/></svg>
      Diğer Eğitim Platformları
    </h2>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <a href="https://yapayzekaokulum.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-secondary/30 hover:bg-warmBg transition-all">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <span class="text-lg">🎓</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Yapay Zeka Okulum</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-mid">Eğitimciler için YZ eğitim platformu</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://gencyz.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-warmBg transition-all">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <span class="text-lg">🧒</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">GençYZ</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-mid">Çocuklar için yapay zeka eğitimi</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://yz-araclari.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-secondary/30 hover:bg-warmBg transition-all">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <span class="text-lg">🛠️</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors">YZ Araçları</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-mid">Yapay zeka araçları rehberi</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://akademikyz.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-accent/30 hover:bg-warmBg transition-all">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <span class="text-lg">📚</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">ScholarAI</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-mid">Akademik araştırma asistanı</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://altunmurat.wordpress.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-warmBg transition-all">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <span class="text-lg">📝</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-dark group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Blog</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-mid">Kişisel blog yazıları</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
